{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act22side_level_act22side_08_beg","storyGroup":"act22side","storySort":16,"storyDependence":"act22side_level_act22side_st02","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"FC-8","storyName":"她的影子","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"为躲避搜捕，苇草带着众人躲入废墟，随后意外发现这里正是传说中的塔拉王城的遗址。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act22side/level_act22side_08_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act22side_08","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":14,"next":16,"characters":["塔拉流民","苇草","莫兰","拉芙希妮","“领袖”","爱布拉娜"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Dialog","id":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_black","screenadapt":"showall","id":5},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":6},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"$darkness01_loop","volume":"0.4","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":9},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"“我将我的心迹写入诗韵。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":10},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"“你啊，将到来的混沌时代中的你。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":11},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"“会知道我的灵魂是如何将其追寻。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":12},{"type":"subtitle","id":13},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":14},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":15},{"type":"Dialog","id":16},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":17},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":18},{"type":"Character","id":19},{"type":"Background","image":"34_g7_galekingruins","screenadapt":"coverall","id":20},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":21},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":22},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":23},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_242","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":24},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":25},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"我就知道，他们不会来这堆被天灾砸烂的石头里面找人。","id":26,"figure":"avg_npc_242"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"多亏早上起了那么大的雾，不然咱们还没这么容易脱身。","id":27,"figure":"avg_npc_242"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":28},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"啊，小心。我们毕竟没有防护装备，在这里受伤的话，是有感染风险的。","id":29,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":30},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0","id":31},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":32},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"莫兰，你也是。源石多发环境，对感染者来说更加危险。","id":33,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":34},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"好，我会注意的。","id":35,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":36},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......凯莉睡着了？","id":37,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":38},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"是，应该只是睡了，不是昏迷，我能感觉到她的呼吸还很平稳。睡着能让她少受一些痛苦。","id":39,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#3$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":40},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"......但我还是怕，再不停下来处理凯莉的伤势的话，她撑不过去。","id":41,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#3$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1","focus":"2","id":42},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"嗯。","id":43,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......你们，失望吗？","id":44,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1","focus":"1","id":45},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"不会的。你不是说过了吗？我们现在不得不和一些深池士兵战斗，是因为他们不想要第二位“领袖”。","id":46,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"但他们还有更大的目标，不会一直追捕我们的。","id":47,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"现在这样逃亡的生活，我们也已经习惯了，可以忍耐下去。","id":48,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1","focus":"1","id":49},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"不过在那之后呢？你还没有告诉过我们你的想法。","id":50,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1","focus":"2","id":51},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......","id":52,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我还没有把握，抱歉。","id":53,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"对了，废墟深处，也许有源石晶簇少一些的地方，我想去看看，能不能找到一个暂时的藏身处。","id":54,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":55},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.7","id":56},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":57},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"大家都应该停下来休息一下了。","id":58,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":59},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"可那个方向，是不是有人在？","id":60,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#3$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":61},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"虽然看上去只是普通人，可我们应该也要躲开。就像你之前说的一样，这种地方有人出没，太异常了，一定要小心......","id":62,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#3$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":63},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......","id":64,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#3$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1","focus":"2","id":65},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......不用。","id":66,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1","focus":"1","id":67},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"......你看起来很害怕。怎么了？","id":68,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":69},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"没关系，不用担心我。","id":70,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":71},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0","id":72},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","id":73},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"（......她来过这里？在这附近？）","id":74,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_242","id":75},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"哎，那边的人，走路的样子是不是有些奇怪？","id":76,"figure":"avg_npc_242"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1","id":77},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"别看。","id":78,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_242","id":79},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":80},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"咿——她怎么已经——","id":81,"figure":"avg_npc_242"},{"type":"Dialog","id":82},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1","id":83},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.2","id":84},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":85},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_skill_ignite_cast","volume":"0.6","id":86},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_magic_1","volume":"1","delay":"0.7","id":87},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":88},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":89},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":90},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"她应该，离世有一段时间了。","id":91,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","id":92},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"只是，那种源石技艺操控着这具身体在行动，就像我们之前见到的那些深池士兵一样。","id":93,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#3$1","id":94},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"为什么要操纵一个普通人？","id":95,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1","id":96},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我还不知道。","id":97,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":98},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"——跟我走吧，这些被源石技艺控制的死者，我来应对。","id":99,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":100},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":101},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":102},{"type":"Character","id":103},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_black","screenadapt":"showall","id":104},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":105},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":106},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":107},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":108},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_walk_stage","id":109},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"这里光线很暗，沿着石阶往下走的时候，小心裸露的碎晶簇......莫兰，你背着凯莉方便行动吗？","id":110},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"我没问题。只要你的火一直燃着，我看得见东西。","id":111},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"好。我们尽量往深处走，别发出太大声音。","id":112},{"type":"Dialog","id":113},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":114},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"——","id":115},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"这是......","id":116},{"type":"Dialog","id":117},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.7","id":118},{"type":"Text","text":"......盖尔王的王城？","id":119},{"type":"Dialog","id":120},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":121},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":122},{"type":"Character","id":123},{"type":"PlayMusic","key":"$calm_loop","volume":"0.4","id":124,"musicid":1},{"type":"Background","screenadapt":"showall","image":"34_g8_galekingruins_inside","x":"100","y":"0","xScale":"1.3","yScale":"1.3","id":125},{"type":"backgroundTween","xFrom":"100","yFrom":"0","xTo":"-100","yTo":"0","xScaleFrom":"1.3","yScaleFrom":"1.3","xScaleTo":"1.3","yScaleTo":"1.3","duration":"20","block":"false","id":126},{"type":"curtain","direction":"0","fillfrom":"0","fillto":"0.2","fadetime":"0.1","id":127},{"type":"curtain","direction":"4","fillfrom":"0","fillto":"0.2","fadetime":"0.1","id":128},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":129},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":130},{"type":"Text","text":"对于那业已覆灭的王朝，有人想象它灰石的骸骨间堆满死战不退的将士盔甲，有人声称它仍将黄金的王冠藏匿于古老阴森的机关之下。","id":131},{"type":"Text","text":"有人以现代伦蒂尼姆的高墙去衬托王城的恢弘，以无边的克拉斯德内海比拟英雄时代美德的兴荣，又哀叹它被维多利亚的阴影日渐销蚀。","id":132},{"type":"Text","text":"人们想象这座古城是塔拉悲情的墓碑，怨恨的亡魂。","id":133},{"type":"dialog","id":134},{"type":"Background","image":"34_g8_galekingruins_inside","screenadapt":"showall","fadetime":"2","id":135},{"type":"curtain","direction":"0","fillfrom":"0.2","fillto":"0","fadetime":"3","id":136},{"type":"curtain","direction":"4","fillfrom":"0.2","fillto":"0","fadetime":"3","id":137},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":138},{"type":"Text","text":"但它只是安静地坐在山丘上，袒露出此地未有王城时的核心。","id":139},{"type":"Text","text":"生出野草，爬满藤蔓。","id":140},{"type":"Dialog","id":141},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":142},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_242","id":143},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"这得是多久以前的东西了？五百年？一千年？","id":144,"figure":"avg_npc_242"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","id":145},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"嘘......不要把凯莉吵醒了。","id":146,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_242","id":147},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"抱歉......我只是有点惊讶，不对，太惊讶了。","id":148,"figure":"avg_npc_242"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"说真的，虽然我们年年演的戏目都会讲不同的盖尔王故事，我也知道我们是塔拉王国子民的后代，所以被叫做塔拉人......","id":149,"figure":"avg_npc_242"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","id":150},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"......但以前没有人相信，这一切竟然真的存在。","id":151,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#3$1","id":152},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"甚至还有传说里，熔融了所有塔拉战士的武器、颠覆了王朝命运的熔炉......","id":153,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","id":154},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"......很久以前，我遇到过一个四处寻找吟游诗人的城里人。","id":155,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"他对我说过，传说虽然有许多是后人编造，但那些故事里，一定留下了历史的痕迹。","id":156,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":157},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0","id":158},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1","focus":"1","id":159},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"苇草，你一定知道很多，是不是？","id":160,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1","focus":"2","id":161},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......","id":162,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#4$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1","focus":"1","id":163},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"你不喜欢这里吗？我们进来后，你就一直不说话。","id":164,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#4$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":165},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......或许是吧。","id":166,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"很小的时候，我就经常读着塔拉的传奇故事，直到入睡。","id":167,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"为维多利亚王室写作的人也好，想要留存塔拉文明的人也好，他们总是写，“德拉克的天性是争斗”。","id":168,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":169},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0.5","id":170},{"type":"Text","text":"传说最初率领盖尔氏族的德拉克，烧干河水向南而行，逃离互相厮杀争夺王座的族亲，开拓了塔拉的土地。","id":171},{"type":"Text","text":"传说维多利亚的红龙杀死了塔拉最后一位游牧的德拉克首领，给他牙牙学语的幼子安上盖尔王的头衔。","id":172},{"type":"Text","text":"传说塔拉的德拉克自此囚于宫廷，哪怕“放逐王”抛下王冠行走荒野二十年，归来觐见时仍被在位的至亲杀害。","id":173},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1","id":174},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"塔拉的历史，充满了这样的故事。德拉克的王城里，遍布阴谋与鲜血。","id":175,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","id":176},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"比起憧憬和幻想，我......害怕这里。","id":177,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":178},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","focus":"-1","id":179},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":180},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"我害怕，有朝一日，要与我的姐姐争斗。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":181},{"type":"subtitle","id":182},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":183},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","id":184},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":185},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":186},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":187},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......不过，天灾留下的晶簇，这里几乎看不见。","id":188,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"在这里休息，应该是安全的。","id":189,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_242","id":190},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"那就好。来，莫兰，我帮你把凯莉放下。","id":191,"figure":"avg_npc_242"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","id":192},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"让她躺在这边吧，背风的地方。","id":193,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"这里的墙很坚实，位置也很隐蔽，我们即使在晚上生起火，应该也不会被外面的人注意到。","id":194,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_242","id":195},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"哎，苇草她怎么——","id":196,"figure":"avg_npc_242"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","id":197},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"让她自己去那边看看吧。","id":198,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":199},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":200},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":201},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":202},{"type":"Character","id":203},{"type":"Background","image":"34_g8_galekingruins_inside","screenadapt":"showall","id":204},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":205},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$ghosthunter_intro","key":"$ghosthunter_loop","volume":"0.4","id":206,"musicid":2},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":207},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":208},{"type":"Dialog","id":209},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":210},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"“我放下战士的荣誉，只为以后塔拉的土地不必再被鲜血浸泡，德拉克的同族不必再刀剑相向。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":211},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"“除非有朝一日，红龙的火焰能令死去的战士从熔炉中复生。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":212},{"type":"subtitle","id":213},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":214},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":215},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_cloakmovement","volume":"0.7","id":216},{"type":"Delay","time":"1.5","id":217},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1","id":218},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......","id":219,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":220},{"type":"Character","id":221},{"type":"Text","text":"苇草听见轻微的响动。","id":222},{"type":"Text","text":"她收回了想要触摸眼前生锈设备的手。","id":223},{"type":"Dialog","id":224},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1","id":225},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"它是......活着的？","id":226,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":227},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.5","id":228},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":229},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_226_weed_1#7","afrom":"0","ato":"0.8","duration":"1","end":"true","id":230},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":231},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"它只不过是，谁都可以驱动的东西......有人把它重新点燃了，你为什么要觉得奇怪？","id":232,"figure":"avg_226_weed_1#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":233},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......嗯，她来过了，不奇怪。","id":234,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":235},{"type":"character","id":236},{"type":"Text","text":"透过孔隙，她看到了紫色的火焰。","id":237},{"type":"Dialog","id":238},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1","id":239},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"这里是曾经的王城，她一定会来......也一定会发出嘲笑声吧？传说中的君王，留下的东西，就只是这些而已。","id":240,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"这里燃起了她的火焰，所以附近才会有那么多不得安息的死者。","id":241,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"那只是，在附近迷路渴死的流浪者，无缘无故地被死亡的火焰唤起。","id":242,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_226_weed_1#1","afrom":"0","ato":"0.8","duration":"0","end":"true","id":243},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"不......别靠近。","id":244,"figure":"avg_226_weed_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"你也害怕那簇火吧？","id":245,"figure":"avg_226_weed_1#1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","id":246},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......","id":247,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_226_weed_1#1","afrom":"0","ato":"0.8","duration":"0","end":"true","id":248},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"我看得到，你想熄灭它。","id":249,"figure":"avg_226_weed_1#1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","id":250},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......嗯，它会给许多人带去痛苦。","id":251,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_226_weed_1#1","afrom":"0","ato":"0.8","duration":"0","end":"true","id":252},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"可你真要这么做的话，我不会让你过去。","id":253,"figure":"avg_226_weed_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"她点燃了深池的火。你知道，你没办法再燃起同样的火焰。","id":254,"figure":"avg_226_weed_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"她做了很多坏事，说了很多漂亮的谎言，可是，那些是非做不可的。她号召了成千上万的塔拉人跟随，不挑剔圣人或暴徒，贵族或贱民。","id":255,"figure":"avg_226_weed_1#1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_226_weed_1#7","afrom":"0","ato":"0.8","duration":"0","end":"true","id":256},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"这些，你做不到。","id":257,"figure":"avg_226_weed_1#7"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":258},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"不......我做得到。","id":259,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1","id":260},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我不信，那些牺牲都是必要的，也绝不会相信，塔拉人要得救，只有她的那一种方法可行。","id":261,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_226_weed_1#1","afrom":"0","ato":"0.8","duration":"0","end":"true","id":262},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"可是从很早以前，从橡林郡的那场大火开始，她就已经是领袖。","id":263,"figure":"avg_226_weed_1#1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":264},{"type":"charslot","id":265},{"type":"Text","text":"她想起那个趴在街道上伤痕累累的女孩。自己想拉起她，让她快走，却又害怕自己向她伸手的话，她也会变成一堆灰烬。","id":266},{"type":"Text","text":"姐姐走到了她身边。","id":267},{"type":"Text","text":"你想活下去吗？姐姐问道。","id":268},{"type":"Text","text":"你旁边就是下水道。从那里爬下去，那些可恶的贵族就再也追不上你。","id":269},{"type":"Text","text":"蔓德拉。她从那里逃出来，最终又回到那里。","id":270},{"type":"Dialog","id":271},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_226_weed_1#1","afrom":"0","ato":"0.8","duration":"0","end":"true","id":272},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"而你，你终究没有伸手拉起任何人。","id":273,"figure":"avg_226_weed_1#1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","id":274},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......","id":275,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1","id":276},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"嗯，如果我能够向她伸出手，也许，事情会变得不一样。","id":277,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"如果她真的得救，那她本该知道，除了像那天的纵火者那样，拥有为非作歹的权力......她还有许多路可以走。","id":278,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_226_weed_1#1","afrom":"0","ato":"0.8","duration":"0","end":"true","id":279},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"可实际上，你连自己的力量都害怕，只能让别人来操纵它。","id":280,"figure":"avg_226_weed_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"......所以，连姐姐都对你失望了，更不用说其他人。","id":281,"figure":"avg_226_weed_1#1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1","id":282},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......不，你这么说，不对。你说的都是已经过去的事。","id":283,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":284},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"现在的我，已经握住过他人的手了。","id":285,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我不能说，是我拉起了他们，但他们想要前行的话，我的火，可以烧出道路。哪怕那条路，是他们牵着我走。","id":286,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"她......如果她能看到这一切，她不会失望的。","id":287,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_226_weed_1#1","afrom":"0","ato":"0.8","duration":"0","end":"true","id":288},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“领袖”","text":"你只是，偶然有了同伴。","id":289,"figure":"avg_226_weed_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“领袖”","text":"在他们面前，你表现得能战斗、演说、号召大家......你假装自己有力。","id":290,"figure":"avg_226_weed_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“领袖”","text":"可你其实只是在模仿她。","id":291,"figure":"avg_226_weed_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“领袖”","text":"你只能，成为她的影子。任何手段，她都可以用到极致，而你比她，多出来太多犹豫和软弱。","id":292,"figure":"avg_226_weed_1#1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":293},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":294},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":295},{"type":"charslot","id":296},{"type":"Background","image":"21_G5_victoria_street_n_ruins","screenadapt":"showall","id":297},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":298},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","keep":"true","initamount":"0","amount":"0.7","block":"true","id":299},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":300},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":301},{"type":"Text","text":"她想起那些纵火烧毁塔拉人街区的军官。他们放声嘲笑塔拉人的自以为是，嘲笑几乎不识字的塔拉人竟然抗议橡林郡的法令不公。","id":302},{"type":"Text","text":"她知道，这就是姐姐最后对老师说的，将会发生的事情。","id":303},{"type":"Text","text":"维多利亚人亲手点燃了仇恨的火焰。在烧光一切之前，这场大火不会停下。","id":304},{"type":"Text","text":"别眨眼，姐姐对她说，看清我们的生活是如何一次又一次地被毁去。","id":305},{"type":"Text","text":"在遍地焦黑尸骸中间，掌控死亡之火的德拉克抬手施术。","id":306},{"type":"Text","text":"冰凉的紫火盖过了原本灼烧着死者的烈焰。","id":307},{"type":"Text","text":"其实那死亡的火焰几乎从来没有取走过任何生命。她只是准许他们从灰烬中爬起，在死后得以向烧毁他们家园的人复仇。","id":308},{"type":"Dialog","id":309},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":310},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":311},{"type":"charslot","id":312},{"type":"Background","image":"34_g8_galekingruins_inside","screenadapt":"showall","id":313},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":314},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","keep":"true","initamount":"0","amount":"0","block":"true","id":315},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":316},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":317},{"type":"Dialog","id":318},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":319},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......我不后悔。","id":320,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"过去，我一直觉得她是对的。","id":321,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"“为了最终建成塔拉人理想的国度，我们的生命都可以作为燃料，投入火中......”","id":322,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"在她身边，我一直是这么说的。","id":323,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","id":324},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......可燃料烧尽之后，她的国度里，还剩下谁？","id":325,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我犹豫过，反思过，逃避过......","id":326,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1","id":327},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我不后悔。","id":328,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我逃到了这里，见过了她看不到的人与事。我想说的，一定与她不同。","id":329,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"所以，我也不会再害怕想起她。","id":330,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#4$1","id":331},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我绝不会......困在自己的影子里！","id":332,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#4$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_226_weed_1#7","afrom":"0","ato":"0.8","duration":"0","end":"true","id":333},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“领袖”","text":"认出这座王城时，你不是正在害怕吗？","id":334,"figure":"avg_226_weed_1#7"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“领袖”","text":"我想，你无法回答你的“同伴”你们将去哪里，但心里早已备好答案。","id":335,"figure":"avg_226_weed_1#7"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“领袖”","text":"不变成我的话，你在深池的梦想里，要如何找到自己的位置呢？","id":336,"figure":"avg_226_weed_1#7"},{"type":"Dialog","id":337},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_humanchange","volume":"1","id":338},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1","afrom":"0","ato":"0.8","duration":"1","end":"true","id":339},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":340},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"——拉芙希妮，你想要什么呢？","id":341,"figure":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":342},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":343},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":344},{"type":"Character","id":345},{"type":"Background","image":"21_G6_decisivebattlealley_n","screenadapt":"showall","id":346},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":347},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","keep":"true","initamount":"0","amount":"0.7","block":"true","id":348},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$burningloop1","volume":"0.7","loop":"true","channel":"fire","id":349},{"type":"bgeffect","name":"$eb_deathburning","layer":"1","id":350},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":351},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"2","amount":"0","block":"true","id":352},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":353},{"type":"Text","text":"苇草想起那场大火里走向她们的死者。","id":354},{"type":"Dialog","id":355},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_226_weed_1#2","id":356},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"......快停下......","id":357,"figure":"avg_226_weed_1#2"},{"type":"Dialog","id":358},{"type":"character","id":359},{"type":"Text","text":"他们伤痕累累，面目全非，眼中却仍然燃烧着渴望。","id":360},{"type":"Text","text":"他们完成了对维多利亚军官的复仇，走向为他们燃起火焰的人。","id":361},{"type":"Dialog","id":362},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_226_weed_1#2","id":363},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"不要再向前走了......","id":364,"figure":"avg_226_weed_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_226_weed_1#1","id":365},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"你们应该......得到安息！","id":366,"figure":"avg_226_weed_1#1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":367},{"type":"character","id":368},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":369},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.03","block":"true","id":370},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":371},{"type":"bgeffect","name":"$eb_burn","layer":"2","id":372},{"type":"bgEffect","layer":"1","id":373},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_skill_ignite_cast","volume":"0.7","id":374},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$b_char_fireharm","volume":"0.6","delay":"0.4","id":375},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.8","block":"true","id":376},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":377},{"type":"Text","text":"——反应过来的时候，离她最近的人已经倒在她的面前，空洞的眼眶注视着她。","id":378},{"type":"Text","text":"在她自己一闪而过的炽烈火光之中，死亡的火焰熄灭了。","id":379},{"type":"Dialog","id":380},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":381},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_226_weed_1#2","id":382},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"......对不起，姐姐。对不起......","id":383,"figure":"avg_226_weed_1#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"我，不是有意破坏你的法术......","id":384,"figure":"avg_226_weed_1#2"},{"type":"Dialog","id":385},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0","id":386},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":387},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":388},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"——做得好，拉芙希妮。","id":389,"figure":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":390},{"type":"Character","id":391},{"type":"Text","text":"她在恐惧中抬头。","id":392},{"type":"Text","text":"姐姐第一次对她露出了赞许的微笑。","id":393},{"type":"Dialog","id":394},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1","id":395},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"做得真好。你的火光，如此耀眼。","id":396,"figure":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"我始终在想，你要怎样才肯显露出自己的力量，令他人瞩目？","id":397,"figure":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"再向我展示一次你的才能吧，让我看到，你竟然真有可能将我的火焰逼退。","id":398,"figure":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"你会战胜我吗，我亲爱的妹妹？","id":399,"figure":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":400},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":401},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"1","id":402},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":403},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":404},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":405},{"type":"bgEffect","layer":"2","id":406},{"type":"Image","id":407}],"characters":["塔拉流民","苇草","莫兰","拉芙希妮","“领袖”","爱布拉娜"]}